{"tid":650230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【交友App末日】FB推交友配對功能 搶Tinder、Speed Dating生意","createTime":"2018-05-02T06:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:28.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d524f9601cb92f01852e7bbbd88bd10345582b85","tid":650230,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180502/58142819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58142819&d=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXytU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ff15635e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F58142819&h=e3f6548f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180502/58142819</a><br />\n<br />\n一向擁有交友功能的Facebook最近推出「交友配對」功能，在其平台上增設類似「Tinder」、「陌陌」等約會平台，搶Dating App生意。<br />\n<br />\n被網友稱為「約炮神器」的Tinder母公司Match Group股價重挫22%，市後回升0.65%，報36.95美元。FB股價則升1%，報174.28美元。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook CEO朱克伯格Mark Zuckerberg於開發者大會上表示，fb會推出「交友配對」功能，擺明搶Tinder等交友Dating App生意，用戶可在fb的程式上，在交友平台另設個人資料，然後讓雙方配對，繼續進行通話聯絡，而在交友配對上的對話，跟fb messenger是開的。<br />\n<br />\n交友配對平台上亦可開設活動，讓附合條件的人士參與，變相是在fb上展開Speed Dating活動。<br />\n<br />\n私隱方面，FB個人帳戶和FB交友配對帳戶分開，交友帳戶只會顯示名字，不會有姓氏，同時FB朋友不會顯示在交友配對顯示，即保證用戶能透過交友配對認識「新朋友」。而交友配對的對話當中，不能向對方傳送圖片或網上連接。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFB表示，潛在配對的分析，會根據你的留言喜好、帳戶設定以及共同朋友等等，同時讓用戶透過群組及活動，尋找「romantic interests」"},{"pid":"57567865d33a9592587bcabece93c1c7245061de","tid":650230,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31212a8afbb242f69ed30e8b2dca0ae1330977e","tid":650230,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"淨係識抄同收購競爭對手<br />\n垃圾Facebook我已經del咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e107db960238f11f302ac67475ec4ccad7a6000b","tid":650230,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5615b8353848e9917ffd35e5489e34c00b626054","tid":650230,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a97d56344670ee4796901c3cd77a8c70334396d0","tid":650230,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5615b8353848e9917ffd35e5489e34c00b626054","tid":650230,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"話咗分開， 唔會見到你真身acc內容， 不過fb拎你真身內容做配對， 根據蘋果新聞"},{"pid":"307020bbc73eebb76ac83d04ed47fa09976ebe88","tid":650230,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"中年人用fb玩換妻"},{"pid":"8a65848b092c9a0efdba81b78d4926474e3fbe36","tid":650230,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"307020bbc73eebb76ac83d04ed47fa09976ebe88","tid":650230,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"中年人用fb玩換妻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"私煙"}]}